{"tid":1578284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新戰線： 馬場！！！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-09-18T05:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T08:30:16.000Z","uid":257527,"like":24,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b8bbae16d578a4ffbe5ac1064cab86ea983a5f70","tid":1578284,"uid":257527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:41:34.000Z","msg":"香港賽馬會證實，今天晚上原訂在跑馬地舉行的夜馬賽事，因為害怕抗議者可能會損害馬會員工、顧客和馬匹的安全，所以馬會決定取消賽事。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">多謝何律師先。</span><br />\n<br />\n學生暑假去食彈。<br />\n藍尸仲有得玩馬仔？<br />\n<br />\n機場你禁到。<br />\n跑馬地馬場你禁唔禁到？<br />\n<br />\n馬房對出放teargas!?<br />\n馬仔索一啖，仲跑唔跑得郁！？<br />\n保險唔包，馬會硬食。<br />\n幾十億凍過水，未計你班馬會金主。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>馬會對香港經濟不下於機場<br />\n<br />\nif we burn, you burn with us</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c2eaeab12c3efa5ebcfe4d3b42588ba29a3b3b83","tid":1578284,"uid":257527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:43:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d187f3fb11354829e01a314f06b7c7622e69a943","tid":1578284,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:43:38.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n第五期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1</a><br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPape